  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK586">
<l>tuṟantār paṭivatta rāki yiṟantārāyn </l>
<l>teṉceyiṉuñ cōrvila toṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is a spy who, assuming the appearance of an ascetic, goes into (whatever place he wishes), examines into (all, that is needful), and never discovers himself, whatever may be done to him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
